Title: Some Call Me Bug Catcher
Description:
Ah, young $r, I could use your help. I have raised generations of life here. 

None more my favorite than the ducklings. But my body has grown old and weak... still that does not stop the cycle.

I need you to catch food for my brood.
RewardText:
Oh...  Back so soon?  It only felt like a moment. 

You got the good parts as well!

Firequackers and Pilot are going to love the chitin.
